---
import Layout from "../layout/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Homepage">
  <section class="max-w-3xl space-y-8">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="title-2">Building things on the internet.</h2>
      <p>
        Currently obsessed with distributed systems and making computers talk to
        each other efficiently.
      </p>
      <p>Sometimes I write about it. Mostly I just stare at logs.</p>
      <sub>Last updated: never, probably.</sub>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="title-3">What I'm working on</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>A tiny key-value store written in Zig, for fun and suffering.</li>
        <li>
          A browser extension that removes dark patterns from e-commerce sites.
        </li>
        <li>Getting better at chess (failing).</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="title-3">Things I find interesting</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Type theory and why most programmers ignore it.</li>
        <li>How cities decide where to put bus stops.</li>
        <li>Old Soviet engineering documents.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="title-3">Elsewhere</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github</a></li>
        <li><a href="./journal">notes / blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" rel="noopener noreferrer">reading list</a></li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h3 class="title-3">Say hello</h3>
      <p>
        <span class="text-gruv-aqua-light">hello (at) example (dot) com</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
